News.Title: Accent Microcell Reports 14.5% Revenue Growth in H1
News.Summary: Accent Microcell, an SME company, has reported a revenue of 1.26 billion rupees for the first half of the fiscal year, compared to 1.1 billion rupees in the same period last year. This represents a year-over-year growth of approximately 14.5%.

News.Title: Accent Microcell Reports 17% Increase in H1 Net Profit
News.Summary: Accent Microcell, an SME company, has reported a net profit of 165 million rupees for the first half of the financial year, compared to 141 million rupees in the same period last year. This represents a year-over-year increase of approximately 17%.
